## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023 and does not include studies or findings published after this date. Additionally, while the sources used are reputable, the report does not cover every aspect of vaccine safety research, focusing instead on general safety and efficacy. Further research could provide more detailed insights into specific vaccines or demographic responses.

